Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.05,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}却渐渐辨不清形状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.85,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}若要将恨意驱赶出心房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.44,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}还如何让你把命偿?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.32,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘尘封过往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:25.45,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只为填罪业汪洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.66,OPCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}怨凛冽锋芒
